text: This obsoletes IRM 1.13.9, Statistics of Income, Statistical Editing of Insurance Company Returns.

The content of this IRM section is no longer pertinent because Statistics of Income (SOI) Division only edits insurance company returns at one IRS processing site. If the SOI Director determines additional IRS processing sites will edit these returns, the Directorâ€™s staff will place the relevant information in IRM 3.49, Statistics of Income Processing.
